SHE'S NOT THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN HUT WHERE IT HURTS.

25:09.539 --> 25:10.710
THIS IS WRONG.

25:10.710 --> 25:12.141
THIS IS ALL WRONG.
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

25:12.141 --> 25:15.514
I CAN'T BE THE ONE
THAT TEARS YOU APART
FROM YOUR FAMILY.

25:15.514 --> 25:16.215
NO, YOU'RE NOT!

25:16.215 --> 25:17.046
I'M GONNA DO
THE EXORCISM.

25:17.046 --> 25:18.517
YOU CAN'T DO THAT.
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS.

25:18.517 --> 25:20.590
NO, IT'S NOT.
NOTHING CAN
HAPPEN TO ME.

25:20.590 --> 25:22.521
I'M NOT AFRAID
OF THAT PRIEST.

25:22.521 --> 25:23.923
I'LL JUST...FAKE IT.

25:23.923 --> 25:26.155
I'LL YELL
AND I'LL SCREAM
AND I'LL, "AAAH!"

25:26.155 --> 25:29.959
YOU KNOW, SO THEY
THINK THE DEMON
JUST FLEW OUT OF ME.

25:29.959 --> 25:31.200
SO IT WON'T ACTUALLY WORK?

25:31.200 --> 25:33.563
I MEAN, YOU'RE NOT
GOING TO GET HURT, RIGHT?

25:33.563 --> 25:35.204
IT'LL BE FINE.

25:35.204 --> 25:36.636
Sock: OH, OH, HOLD ON!

25:36.636 --> 25:37.637
THIS THING PLAYS BLU-RAY.

25:37.637 --> 25:40.039
WE GOTTA GO BACK
AND GET THE FLATTIE.

25:42.672 --> 25:44.974
[MUSIC PLAYING,
INDISTINCT CHATTER]

25:44.974 --> 25:47.917
HEY! LOOK WHO I FOUND.

25:48.718 --> 25:49.719
YOU FOUND GLADYS?

25:49.719 --> 25:52.251
YEAH! I PAID HER
TO TRANSLATE
THE DEMON SCROLL

25:52.251 --> 25:53.653
SO THAT YOU CAN GET OUT
OF YOUR DEAL!

25:53.653 --> 25:54.724
YEAH, AND THE METER'S RUNNING,

25:54.724 --> 25:56.626
SO LET'S GET THIS SHOW
ON THE ROAD.

25:56.626 --> 25:59.629
WHAT? WHAT'S WRONG?

26:01.761 --> 26:04.263
THAT WAS IT.
THAT WAS MY CHANCE.

26:04.263 --> 26:05.765
I HAD THE DEVIL
RIGHT WHERE I WANTED HIM,

26:05.765 --> 26:07.637
AND I LET HIM SLIP
THROUGH MY FINGERS.

26:07.637 --> 26:10.099
I'M RIGHT BACK
WHERE I STARTED FROM.

26:10.099 --> 26:10.640
I'M SCREWED.

26:10.640 --> 26:11.941
YEAH, STILL DOESN'T
EXPLAIN THE SUIT.

26:11.941 --> 26:15.304
YOU LOOK LIKE
JUSTIN TIMBERLAKE
TOOK A DUMP.

26:15.304 --> 26:18.608
STEVE GAVE THE SUIT TO ME
AFTER HE TRANSLATED THE SCROLL.

26:18.608 --> 26:19.308
IT SAYS THAT I HAVE
TO DRESS LIKE THE DEVIL.

26:19.308 --> 26:22.912
I HAVE TO REFLECT
HIS APPEARANCE
IN ORDER TO BEAT HIM.

26:22.912 --> 26:24.283
WHAT? IT DOESN'T
SAY THAT.

26:24.283 --> 26:26.115
IT DOESN'T SAY
REFLECT THE DEVIL.

26:26.115 --> 26:29.088
IT SAYS THE DEVIL'S
REFLECTION.

26:29.088 --> 26:31.290
THE DEVIL'S VANITY
IS HIS WEAKNESS.

26:31.290 --> 26:32.822
WHAT YOU SHOULD
HAVE DONE

26:32.822 --> 26:35.194
WAS TAKEN A BIG MIRROR
WITH YOU TO
THE COMPETITION.

26:35.194 --> 26:36.796
YOU KNOW, AS LIKE
A DISTRACTION.

26:36.796 --> 26:39.028
THE DEVIL CAN'T RESIST
LOOKING AT HIMSELF.

26:39.028 --> 26:41.831
WELL, THAT DOESN'T REALLY
DO ME ANY GOOD NOW, DOES IT?

26:41.831 --> 26:44.003
WELL, THERE HAS TO BE
SOME WAY TO CHALLENGE HIM AGAIN.

26:44.003 --> 26:46.636
NO. HE SAID I HAVE
TO MAKE IT WORTH HIS WHILE.

26:46.636 --> 26:49.378
I'VE GOT NOTHING
LEFT TO GIVE HIM.

26:50.239 --> 26:51.841
I'M GETTING ANOTHER DRINK.

26:51.841 --> 26:54.383
Gladys: STEVE,
WHAT A DOPE.

26:54.383 --> 26:57.386
I ALWAYS KNEW
HE COULDN'T READ.

26:57.386 --> 26:59.749
GLADYS, I NEED A FAVOR.

26:59.749 --> 27:03.993
I'M NOT MAKING OUT
WITH YOU!

27:03.993 --> 27:05.194
ALL RIGHT.

27:05.194 --> 27:08.257
I'LL MAKE OUT
WITH YOU.

27:09.999 --> 27:13.632
HOW DO I GET A MEETING
WITH THE DEVIL?

27:17.266 --> 27:18.808
[EXHALES] HEY.

27:18.808 --> 27:19.709
YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

27:19.709 --> 27:21.410
'CAUSE WE DON'T HAVE TO
IF YOU DON'T--

27:21.410 --> 27:23.142
NO, I'M SURE.
OK.

27:23.142 --> 27:25.314
HI, MIJO.
HEY, GRANDMA.

27:25.314 --> 27:27.376
YOU REMEMBER
FATHER O'MALLEY?

27:27.376 --> 27:28.347
HELLO.
HI.

27:28.347 --> 27:29.919
CAN I GET YOU ANYTHING?

27:29.919 --> 27:31.650
UH, SODA, WATER?

27:31.650 --> 27:33.823
UH, NO, I'M FINE.
THANK YOU.

27:33.823 --> 27:35.685
I WOULD LOVE A BEER.

27:35.685 --> 27:38.087
WHAT? FATHER'S GONNA
KNOCK THIS OUT,

27:38.087 --> 27:39.058
NO PROBLEM, RIGHT, FATHER?

27:39.058 --> 27:40.930
HA HA, I CAN'T MAKE
ANY PROMISES,

27:40.930 --> 27:44.063
BUT I HOPE TO, YES.

27:44.063 --> 27:46.295
SO, NINA, WHY DON'T
YOU AND I HEAD UPSTAIRS

27:46.295 --> 27:48.297
AND GET STARTED,
SHALL WE?

27:48.297 --> 27:50.840
OK, YEAH.

28:09.819 --> 28:11.420
Nina: DEAR BEN,

28:11.420 --> 28:12.461
I WANT YOU TO KNOW
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOU

28:12.461 --> 28:16.425
AND HOW SPECIAL
THESE LAST FEW MONTHS
WITH YOU HAVE BEEN.

28:16.425 --> 28:17.196
BUT I LIED.

28:17.196 --> 28:20.369
THERE'S A GOOD CHANCE
THAT THIS EXORCISM
WILL WORK,

28:20.369 --> 28:22.271
AND IF THAT HAPPENS,
I'LL BE SENT BACK TO HELL.

28:22.271 --> 28:25.875
I'M SORRY THAT I DIDN'T
TELL YOU THAT THIS WAS
A POSSIBILITY,

28:25.875 --> 28:28.137
BUT ULTIMATELY,
I COULDN'T ACCEPT THE FACT

28:28.137 --> 28:31.210
THAT I WAS THE REASON
YOU WERE NO LONGER
A PART OF YOUR FAMILY.

28:31.210 --> 28:33.212
AND IF WE NEVER
SEE EACH OTHER AGAIN,

28:33.212 --> 28:36.145
I WILL THINK ABOUT YOU
EVERY DAY.

28:36.145 --> 28:39.148
LOVE ALWAYS, NINA.

28:48.457 --> 28:50.830
[CROAKING]

28:50.830 --> 28:52.862
ALL RIGHT,
DON'T YOU WORRY, KIDDIES.

28:52.862 --> 28:55.464
SOCK'S ON HIS WAY
TO SAVE YOUR ASSES.

28:55.464 --> 28:57.066
HERE WE GO!

28:57.066 --> 28:58.207
AHH.

28:58.207 --> 28:59.809
OH.

28:59.809 --> 29:01.310
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

29:01.310 --> 29:03.442
IT GOT SO HOT IN HERE!

29:04.513 --> 29:07.516
AHH. OHH.

29:07.516 --> 29:10.119
[INHALING]

29:10.119 --> 29:12.281
OH, WHAT'S GOING ON?

29:12.281 --> 29:14.053
WHAT IS WRONG WITH ME?!

29:14.053 --> 29:15.384
COME ON!

29:21.190 --> 29:23.132
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

29:23.132 --> 29:25.134
HI.

29:25.134 --> 29:27.236
CAN I HAVE
A SECOND WITH HER?

29:27.236 --> 29:30.299
OH, CERTAINLY.

29:33.142 --> 29:34.473
HEY.
HI.

29:34.473 --> 29:38.207
SO PUT ON A GOOD SHOW,
ALL RIGHT?

29:38.207 --> 29:40.810
OK.
ALL RIGHT.

29:40.810 --> 29:43.482
BEN, WAIT.
YEAH?

29:43.482 --> 29:45.915
I LOVE YOU.

29:45.915 --> 29:48.517
AWW, THAT'S SWEET.

29:49.158 --> 29:51.160
BREAK A LEG, YOU TWO!

29:52.822 --> 29:55.324
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]

30:06.936 --> 30:08.137
Grandma: SOCK, SOCK!

30:08.137 --> 30:09.538
OK!

30:09.538 --> 30:12.441
WHOA, WHOA!

30:16.185 --> 30:17.016
OK.

30:17.016 --> 30:18.147
Grandma: [SPEAKING SPANISH]

30:18.147 --> 30:19.548
WHY DO I KEEP
TRIPPING OUT?

30:19.548 --> 30:22.922
OH, TOO MUCH [INDISTINCT]

30:24.023 --> 30:26.155
SAM? NO!

30:26.155 --> 30:29.028
[GRANDMA YELLING INDISTINCTLY]

30:30.199 --> 30:31.400
NO WAY!

30:31.400 --> 30:34.303
[YELLING INDISTINCTLY]

30:34.303 --> 30:36.105
YOU'RE NOT GONNA STOP ME!

30:36.105 --> 30:38.167
I WILL NOT BE STOPPED!

30:39.138 --> 30:40.870
[DISTORTED YELLING]

30:40.870 --> 30:42.171
[YELLING]

30:42.171 --> 30:44.543
OH, HER MAGIC IS STRONG!

30:44.543 --> 30:47.516
BUT I AM STRONGER.

30:49.949 --> 30:50.880
[DISTORTED YELLING]

30:50.880 --> 30:53.883
[TIRES SQUEALING]
DIE, YOU PINT-SIZED WITCH!

30:56.125 --> 31:00.029
Father O'Malley: MOST GLORIOUS
PRINCE OF THE HEAVENLY ARMIES,

31:00.029 --> 31:02.461
MICHAEL, THE ARCHANGEL,
DEFEND US

31:02.461 --> 31:06.495
IN OUR BATTLE AGAINST
THE RULERS OF DARKNESS.

31:06.495 --> 31:09.368
AAH!
[SIZZLING]

31:10.239 --> 31:13.372
MOUTH IS SO DRY.

31:13.372 --> 31:17.176
MY MOUTH IS SO DRRRYYY.

31:17.176 --> 31:19.248
[GROANING]

31:19.248 --> 31:20.980
WHAT DA HELL?

31:20.980 --> 31:22.551
OH, MY GOD!

31:22.551 --> 31:24.653
[FATHER O'MALLEY
AND NINA SCREAMING]

31:24.653 --> 31:26.916
Father O'Malley:
HELL SPAWN!

31:26.916 --> 31:30.459
THE BLOOD OF THE MARTYRS COMPELS
ME!

31:30.459 --> 31:32.591
SOUNDS LIKE IT'S
GOING PRETTY WELL.

31:32.591 --> 31:34.363
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

31:34.363 --> 31:35.664
I'LL GET IT. AHH.

31:35.664 --> 31:38.197
[SOCK GROANING]
WHOA, SOCK!

31:38.197 --> 31:41.971
[MUFFLED] THERE'S SOMETHING
WRONG WITH MY MOUTH!

31:41.971 --> 31:43.102
WHAT?

31:43.102 --> 31:45.204
[INDISTINCT]

31:45.204 --> 31:48.137
[NINA SCREAMING]

31:48.137 --> 31:49.078
[MUFFLED] NINA!

31:49.078 --> 31:51.480
SOCK--SOCK--
HEY, SOCK!

31:51.480 --> 31:53.242
[SCREAMING]

31:53.242 --> 31:55.444
THE BLOOD
OF THE MARINERS
COMPELS ME!

31:55.444 --> 31:57.616
AAH! [MUFFLED YELLING]

31:57.616 --> 32:01.520
[MUFFLED]
IN THE NAME
OF GOD! AHH!

32:01.520 --> 32:03.222
WHO ARE YOU?

32:03.222 --> 32:04.553
MENUDO.

32:04.553 --> 32:06.595
BENJAMIN,
GET HIM
OUT OF HERE!

32:06.595 --> 32:08.597
NO, NO, NO!

32:08.597 --> 32:12.501
[INDISTINCT]

32:16.205 --> 32:19.068
[MUFFLED] AND BEN,
NINA LOVES YOU SO MUCH,

32:19.068 --> 32:21.370
LOVES YOU FOREVER!

32:21.370 --> 32:23.112
[INDISTINCT]

32:23.112 --> 32:26.175
UH, HEY, GUYS,
I THINK IT'S GONE.

32:26.175 --> 32:27.076
[SOCK SINGING]

32:27.076 --> 32:28.117
WELL,
HOW DO YOU FEEL?

32:28.117 --> 32:31.120
I FEEL GOOD.
BUT I THINK YOU SHOULD
WORRY ABOUT HIM.

32:31.120 --> 32:32.621
I THINK THE DEMON JUMPED.

32:32.621 --> 32:35.454
[SINGING INDISTINCTLY]

32:38.127 --> 32:41.630
OH, SO NOW IT RESIDES
IN THIS POOR MAN,

32:41.630 --> 32:42.961
DOES IT?
[MUMBLING]

32:42.961 --> 32:46.235
IF YOU WANT TO DANCE, DEMON,
YOU'LL DANCE WITH ME!

32:46.235 --> 32:48.197
OHH, YEAH!

32:48.197 --> 32:49.268
[THUD]

32:49.268 --> 32:51.170
SORRY, SOCK!

32:55.244 --> 32:58.077
I NEED YOUR OPINION, SAMMY.

32:58.077 --> 32:59.278
ON MY LAPEL,
WHICH DO YOU THINK

32:59.278 --> 33:01.350
MAKES MY EYES POP MORE, HUH?

33:01.350 --> 33:04.083
CARNATION OR LILY?

33:04.083 --> 33:05.384
I KNOW, BOTH, RIGHT?

33:05.384 --> 33:10.089
THAT'S THE BEAUTY
OF WEARING A DARK SUIT
AND HAVING THIS FACE.

33:10.089 --> 33:11.360
GO AWAY.

33:11.360 --> 33:14.063
OH, WHY THE BIG FROWN?

33:14.063 --> 33:16.125
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE
ON CLOUD NINE.

33:16.125 --> 33:17.296
WHY WOULD YOU
THINK THAT?

33:17.296 --> 33:19.768
YOU AND ME,
QUARTERS REMATCH.

33:19.768 --> 33:23.102
IT'S ALL SET UP.

33:23.302 --> 33:24.433
YOU DIDN'T KNOW?

33:24.433 --> 33:25.734
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

33:25.734 --> 33:28.077
SOMEONE MADE IT
WORTH MY WHILE.

33:28.077 --> 33:29.778
SO THE CONTEST IS BACK ON.

33:29.778 --> 33:31.240
SOMEONE? WHO?

33:31.240 --> 33:33.782
YOUR GIRL. ANDI.

33:34.343 --> 33:37.015
SHE PUT UP HER OWN SOUL
AS COLLATERAL.

33:37.015 --> 33:38.317
SHE MUST REALLY BE INTO YOU.

33:38.317 --> 33:41.019
YOU'RE A LUCKY GUY.

33:48.026 --> 33:49.698
TELL ME
YOU DIDN'T DO IT.

33:49.698 --> 33:52.631
AHH, YEAH, I KINDA DID.

33:52.631 --> 33:55.234
ANDI...WHAT WERE YOU
THINKING?

33:55.234 --> 33:58.067
I WAS THINKING
THAT I WANT YOU
OUT OF YOUR DEAL.

33:58.067 --> 33:59.368
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY
TO DO IT.

33:59.368 --> 34:00.539
NO, YOU HAVE
TO STOP IT.

34:00.539 --> 34:01.670
YOU HAVE TO GO BACK
TO THE DEVIL

34:01.670 --> 34:04.213
AND TELL HIM
YOU CHANGED YOUR MIND.

34:04.213 --> 34:05.174
NO.

34:05.174 --> 34:06.715
NO, I WANT TO DO THIS.

34:06.715 --> 34:10.179
I NEED TO DO THIS.

34:10.179 --> 34:11.150
I BELIEVE IN YOU.

34:11.150 --> 34:13.051
AND I BELIEVE
THAT YOU CAN BEAT HIM.

34:13.051 --> 34:15.454
AND I'M TIRED
OF BEING ALONE.

34:15.454 --> 34:16.655
AREN'T YOU?

34:16.655 --> 34:18.127
IT'S TOO MUCH TO RISK.

34:18.127 --> 34:21.630
WELL, IT'S MY RISK TO TAKE.

34:22.361 --> 34:25.494
WE'RE GONNA BEAT
THE DEVIL, SAM!

34:25.494 --> 34:27.596
I KNOW IT.

34:27.596 --> 34:29.698
COME ON.

34:43.552 --> 34:44.813
Sam: ARE YOU NERVOUS?

34:44.813 --> 34:46.515
Andi: YEAH.
ARE YOU?

34:46.515 --> 34:49.258
YEAH.
[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING]

34:49.258 --> 34:51.220
THIS IS FOR
THE LADY'S FILE.

34:51.220 --> 34:52.861
IT'S NOT EVERY DAY
I GET TO WIN

34:52.861 --> 34:54.863
SUCH A BEAUTIFUL TROPHY.

34:54.863 --> 34:57.226
YEAH, WE'LL SEE ABOUT THAT.

34:57.226 --> 35:00.569
I'M ALREADY LIKING
THE WOMAN'S TOUCH.

35:00.569 --> 35:01.500
VERY NICE, ANDI.

35:01.500 --> 35:03.602
REALLY SPRUCES
THE PLACE UP.

35:03.602 --> 35:05.674
SAM, JUST GET THIS
OVER WITH.

35:05.674 --> 35:07.406
YEAH, SAMMY.

35:07.406 --> 35:09.408
LET'S DO GET THIS OVER WITH.

35:09.408 --> 35:13.111
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
ANDI BROUGHT TO THE PARTY.

35:15.384 --> 35:18.417
THIS TIME I THINK
YOU SHOULD GO FIRST.

35:20.849 --> 35:26.425
NOW I KNOW YOU'RE THE BRAINS
OF THIS WHOLE OPERATION.

35:27.196 --> 35:28.897
YOUR TURN.

36:10.899 --> 36:13.342
SAM, ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS GET TWO IN.

36:13.342 --> 36:15.704
YOU GOT THIS.

36:18.377 --> 36:19.378
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

36:19.378 --> 36:22.251
I'M A BAD LOSER,
ALL RIGHT?

36:22.251 --> 36:23.752
AND IF YOU SHOULD
EVENTUALLY WIN THIS THING,

36:23.752 --> 36:24.853
DON'T EXCEPT ANY HUGS
OR GRAB-ASS.

36:24.853 --> 36:29.618
THERE'S SHOT GLASSES
IN HOUSEWARES.
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

36:33.762 --> 36:35.224
HEY, BUDDY.

36:35.224 --> 36:36.665
STEVE, HEY.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

36:36.665 --> 36:41.700
I HEARD SOME BONEHEAD
SCREWED UP AN ANCIENT
TRANSLATION.

36:41.700 --> 36:42.471
GUILTY.

36:42.471 --> 36:43.732
AH, DON'T WORRY
ABOUT IT, MAN.

36:43.732 --> 36:46.335
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT A MENSCH YOU ARE?

36:46.335 --> 36:47.436
THANKS. LISTEN,
I GOTTA GO.

36:47.436 --> 36:49.378
I'M ABOUT TO GET OUT OF
MY DEAL WITH THE DEVIL.

36:49.378 --> 36:51.440
I KNOW. I HEARD.

36:51.440 --> 36:53.842
AND LET ME JUST SAY

36:53.842 --> 36:56.245
HOW TRULY, DEEPLY

36:56.245 --> 36:58.517
SORRY I AM.

36:58.917 --> 37:00.619
SORRY FOR WHAT?

37:00.619 --> 37:03.552
[CRUNCH]
AAH!

37:05.524 --> 37:07.726
SAM, I'M SO SORRY.

37:07.726 --> 37:08.927
WHY?

37:08.927 --> 37:13.932
IT'S FOR THE BEST.
THAT'S ALL I KNOW.

37:18.407 --> 37:19.438
OH, MY GOD!

37:19.438 --> 37:20.739
SAM, WHAT HAPPENED?

37:20.739 --> 37:22.511
IT'S BROKEN.
WHAT?!

37:22.511 --> 37:22.841
HOW?

37:22.841 --> 37:24.373
I CAN'T TALK
ABOUT IT RIGHT NOW.

37:24.373 --> 37:26.515
HEY, SAMMY, COME ON,
IF YOU WANTED TO FORFEIT,

37:26.515 --> 37:28.246
ALL YOU HAD TO DO
WAS SAY SO.

37:28.246 --> 37:29.247
NO.

37:29.247 --> 37:31.350
NO FORFEIT.

37:38.287 --> 37:40.789
OH, MAN.
THAT'S PATHETIC.

37:40.789 --> 37:42.631
COME ON.
JUST STOP RIGHT NOW,

37:42.631 --> 37:44.293
PLEASE? FOR YOUR OWN SAKE.

37:44.293 --> 37:47.696
I STILL HAVE
ONE GOOD HAND.

37:53.342 --> 37:54.943
NOT A LEFTY, HUH?

37:54.943 --> 37:56.605
SHUT UP.

37:56.605 --> 37:59.408
[CHUCKLES]

38:01.510 --> 38:03.712
[DEVIL LAUGHING]

38:03.952 --> 38:06.615
OH, THIS IS HARD TO WATCH.

38:20.529 --> 38:23.301
[CHUCKLES]

38:26.475 --> 38:27.676
SO...

38:27.676 --> 38:32.441
LET'S JUST TAKE A SURVEY
WHO HAD THE WORST WEEK.

38:32.441 --> 38:35.083
I LOST MY SOUL TO THE DEVIL.

38:35.083 --> 38:37.616
TOP THAT.

38:37.916 --> 38:40.088
AN ANGEL BROKE MY HAND
IN 6 PLACES,

38:40.088 --> 38:42.551
WHICH EVIDENTLY MEANS
HEAVEN HATES ME,

38:42.551 --> 38:44.553
AND THE DEVIL
STILL OWNS MY SOUL.

38:44.553 --> 38:47.356
OK, LET'S RECAP
THE SOCK.

38:47.356 --> 38:48.827
I GOT FROG-ROOFIED.

38:48.827 --> 38:50.799
MY MOUTH
TASTES LIKE SAND.

38:50.799 --> 38:52.361
MY MIND IS MELTING.

38:52.361 --> 38:53.702
I TASTED MUSIC,

38:53.702 --> 38:57.335
AND IT TASTED
LIKE GARBAGE.

38:58.837 --> 39:00.909
I HAD A PRETTY
GOOD WEEK.

39:00.909 --> 39:01.810
WHAT?

39:01.810 --> 39:04.112
SOCK SAVED MY GIRLFRIEND
FROM GOING BACK TO HELL.

39:04.112 --> 39:05.744
YEAH.
THANK YOU.

39:05.744 --> 39:07.976
I REALLY HATE
YOUR GRANDMOTHER.

39:07.976 --> 39:09.418
I KNOW.
YEAH.

39:09.418 --> 39:12.421
Sock: I NEED TO GET
FRUIT ON MY PANCAKES.

39:12.421 --> 39:14.853
Ben: SURE.
WHIPPED CREAM, MAYBE.

39:14.853 --> 39:16.825
SURE.

39:18.627 --> 39:20.128
OH.

39:20.128 --> 39:21.430
SO...

39:21.430 --> 39:25.133
I'M REALLY SORRY
THAT YOUR SOUL GOT
DAMNED FOR ETERNITY.

39:25.133 --> 39:28.136
THAT'S...
THAT'S A BUMMER.

39:28.136 --> 39:30.098
LET'S--COME HERE.
THANKS.

39:30.098 --> 39:33.001
OHH.

39:35.444 --> 39:36.144
I'M SORRY.

39:36.144 --> 39:37.746
THANK YOU.

39:37.746 --> 39:39.478
SHOTGUN.

39:39.478 --> 39:41.550
Ben: AHH!

39:41.550 --> 39:44.853
LOOK, ANDI, I WANT YOU
TO KNOW I FEEL TERRIBLE

39:44.853 --> 39:47.085
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED.
YOU PUT YOURSELF ON THE LINE,

39:47.085 --> 39:49.958
YOU PUT YOUR SOUL
ON THE LINE,

39:49.958 --> 39:51.019
AND I LET YOU DOWN.

39:51.019 --> 39:53.021
I DON'T EXPECT YOU
TO FORGIVE ME.

39:53.021 --> 39:55.964
I JUST...
I HOPE THAT--

40:04.933 --> 40:07.035
WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

40:07.035 --> 40:10.078
THE DEVIL
OWNS MY SOUL.

40:10.078 --> 40:13.742
BUT I DON'T...

40:13.742 --> 40:16.184
FEEL ANY DIFFERENT.
YOU KNOW?

40:16.184 --> 40:20.689
AND I STILL
LOVE YOU MORE
THAN I EVER DID.

40:21.850 --> 40:24.092
AS BAD AS THIS
ALL SEEMS,

40:24.092 --> 40:28.096
I'M...I'M REALLY HAPPY.

40:28.096 --> 40:30.859
IS THAT WEIRD?

40:30.859 --> 40:32.100
YES. COMPLETELY.

40:32.100 --> 40:34.963
WE CAN STILL TRY
TO GET OUT OF OUR
DEALS WITH THE DEVIL

40:34.963 --> 40:37.435
AND WE CAN TRY
TO CHANGE OUR FATES.

40:37.435 --> 40:39.838
WE DID IT ONCE BEFORE,
AND WE CAN TRY AGAIN.

40:39.838 --> 40:44.142
OK, IF NOTHING ELSE,
THEN WE HAVE TIME TOGETHER.

40:44.142 --> 40:46.945
THEN I'M HAPPY, TOO.

40:49.578 --> 40:52.220
Steve:
THEN I'M HAPPY, TOO.

40:53.221 --> 40:54.783
STEVE,
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

40:54.783 --> 40:56.955
I THOUGHT I OVERHEARD YOU
SAY YOU WERE HAPPY.

40:56.955 --> 40:59.157
I FIGURED IT WOULD BE
A GOOD TIME TO POKE IN.

40:59.157 --> 41:00.088
GET OUT!

41:00.088 --> 41:02.130
LOOK, I'M NOT EXACTLY
PLEASED

41:02.130 --> 41:04.793
WITH THE WAY THINGS
TURNED OUT, EITHER, BUT--

41:04.793 --> 41:05.994
HEY, OW! OW!

41:05.994 --> 41:07.966
ANDI, ARE YOU
THROWING ROCKS AT ME?

41:07.966 --> 41:09.898
YEAH, I'M TRYING
TO BREAK YOUR HAND!

41:09.898 --> 41:12.971
HEY! SAM, WOULD YOU PLEASE
TELL HER TO QUIT IT?

41:12.971 --> 41:15.003
OW! WOULD YOU LET ME EXPLAIN?!

41:15.003 --> 41:17.576
FINE, FINE, EXPLAIN.
WHAT'S YOUR EXPLANATION?

41:17.576 --> 41:20.078
I'M ACTING ON ORDERS
FROM UPSTAIRS.

41:20.078 --> 41:25.213
I DON'T KNOW EXACTLY WHY
THEY HAD ME DO THE THINGS
THAT THEY HAD ME DO.

41:25.213 --> 41:26.254
GUYS!

41:26.254 --> 41:27.786
STOP! STOP!

41:27.786 --> 41:29.157
YOU HAVE A RIGHT
TO BE UPSET,

41:29.157 --> 41:33.091
BUT THROWING ROCKS
IS NEVER CONSTRUCTIVE.

41:33.091 --> 41:35.664
ENOUGH!

41:36.925 --> 41:39.698
YEAH, I GOT MY WINGS
EARLIER TODAY.

41:39.698 --> 41:41.169
I WANTED IT TO BE A SURPRISE.

41:41.169 --> 41:45.003
YOU GOT YOUR WINGS
BECAUSE YOU BROKE
MY HAND?

41:45.003 --> 41:46.735
THAT'S GREAT.
CONGRATULATIONS.

41:46.735 --> 41:49.237
IT'S BECAUSE OF
HOW I HELPED YOU.

41:49.237 --> 41:50.008
HELPED?

41:50.008 --> 41:52.510
THE DEVIL OWNS
BOTH OF OUR SOULS!

41:52.510 --> 41:55.243
HEAVEN WORKS
IN MYSTERIOUS WAYS, ANDI.

41:55.243 --> 41:57.916
YOU'VE GOT TO BELIEVE.

41:57.916 --> 41:59.087
BELIEVE WHAT?

41:59.087 --> 42:01.750
THAT YOU ARE NOT ALONE.
